    Unleash Your Inner Ninja

    Prepare to step into the shadows with the deadliest guardian of light. In this electrifying new action-2D platformer, a fierce kunoichi girl ninja warrior must harness her ancient clan's techniques to battle a relentless onslaught of evil.

    Master a fluid combat system, unleashing dazzling combos, shuriken storms, and silent takedowns against hordes of cunning baddies. Each level builds toward an epic confrontation with a unique, monstrous boss, testing your skill and strategy to the limit. The balance between good and evil rests in your hands. Sharpen your blades and steady your resolvethe fight for justice arrives soon on mobile app stores.
